subject: Complaint
content: I just try to get on the 7 bus route from Parker. I waved down the bus who started to slow down and pull over, then he drove off without picking me up. I'm tired of these bus drivers doing this. I've had a time before were another busdriver was just gonna drive on pass if I didn't wave him down.Tyler BannerApp Name: Capital MetroApp Version : 4.31.2 1057OS Version : 11Get Outlook for Android
